    "One would probably even find some journal articles that present a tool in detail and that make the software available (e.g., Komogortsev et al., 2010; Nyström & Holmqvist, 2010; Hein & Zangemeister, 2017; Hessels et al., 2017; van Renswoude et al., 2018).",
    "However, at first glance, many of these tools may appear to be hard to use.",
